songs.title: Let You In
songs.lyrics:
[Intro: Azealia Banks]
You're now listening
To a Rihanna exclusive
And now that I have your attention
I'm going to keep it
Psychosomatic, addict, insane
Psychosomatic, addict, insane

[Intro: Rihanna]
She's breaking out to go on an adventure

[Hook: Azealia Banks]
Fly with me through in space and time
Through the constellations, light your life
Bet the sight'll leave you starry eyed
In my mind, imma let you in (x3)

Gonna let you in, I'm gonna let you in
I'm gonna let you in, I'm gonna let you hear

I am so free
I am so free
I am so free
So glad to have you here

Fly with me through in space and time
Through the constellations, light your life
Bet the sight'll leave you starry eyed
I'm so glad that I have you here
That I have you here, glad that I have you here

My only thing is to find myself and live my life from my heart, from my soul, and that's the message that I want little girls to get from me, I want them to know that it's the only way they'll really be happy, happy happy

Happy, happy, happy 

Gonna let you in, I'm gonna let you in
I'm gonna let you in, I'm gonna let you hear
